  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>Administrator System Health provides comprehensive monitoring and management of platform performance, resource utilization, error tracking, and overall system status. This includes real-time metrics, performance analytics, error monitoring, resource management, and proactive health assessment to ensure optimal platform operation and user experience.</p>

  <h3>Access Requirements</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Administrator Role</strong> — Must be logged in with admin privileges</li>
    <li><strong>System Monitoring</strong> — Authority to monitor system performance and health</li>
    <li><strong>Resource Management</strong> — Access to resource utilization and capacity planning</li>
    <li><strong>Error Analysis</strong> — Ability to analyze system errors and performance issues</li>
    <li><strong>Direct Access</strong> — Available via `/admin/system-health`</li>
  </ul>

